text: This is a list of diffuse nebulae. Most nebulae are diffuse, meaning they do not have well-defined boundaries. Types of diffuse nebulae include emission nebulae and reflection nebulae ==Emission and reflection nebulae== ==See also== *Lists of astronomical objects *List of nebulae Diffuse nebulae *Diffuse list *Diffuse list
